summary: This is a small collection of Floor tiles I put together and I'm using some in my upcoming player home mod Fall Manor.
descriptionHtml:
[center][/center][center][img]http://i60.tinypic.com/i3b3w9.jpg[/img]

[img]http://i68.tinypic.com/29fv0af.jpg[/img]

This is a small collection of Floor tiles I put together and I'm using some in my upcoming player home mod Fall Manor.

These Custom Meshes and Textures are free to use by any one as long as I am credited for my work.

If you would like to Check these Resources out in-game you need to open the console with the "Tild Key" and type coc srsfloor01.



[color=#00ffff][size=5][b][color=#6fa8dc]This mod and all Other mods by me are Nexus Exclusive and are not to be uploaded to any other website what so ever.[/color][/b][/size][/color]

[img]http://i62.tinypic.com/2m68tgz.jpg[/img]
[font=Arial][size=3]
[/size][/font][b][color=#ffd966][size=5]Anyone that would like to translate this mod for other languages has my Express permission as long as they do not upload it to other sites or edit any aspect of this mod.[/size][/color][/b][/center][center][b][color=#ffd966][size=4][/size][/color][/b][font=Arial][size=3]
